            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1610980779384-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tortilla is in the oven, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> ultimate vegan burger patties</strong> to the pan breaking them up with a wooden spoon as you go (as you would mince)</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
