    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic </strong>and chop the<strong> cornichons </strong>roughly</p><p>Once the vegan mince is beginning to crisp, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
