      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>tortilla triangles</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then top with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>vegan mince</strong> and tear over <strong>half </strong>the <strong>vegan cheese</strong></p><p>Then repeat one more layer and put the dish in the oven for 3-4 min or until the vegan cheese has melted</p>",
